<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4272597>
    dc:description "Fig. 64. Leiodes okawai Nakane, 1963.A – body, dorsal view; B – ditto, lateral view; C – antenna; D – elytral punctures; E – mesoventrite, lateral view; F – male metaventrite; G – female metaventrite. Scale I: 1 mm for A and B; II: 0.5 mm for C; III: 0.5 mm for E; IV: 1 mm for F and G." ;
