<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4272517>
    dc:description "Fig. 24. Leiodes yoshitakei sp. nov. A – body, dorsal view; B – ditto, lateral view; C – dorsal color; D – antenna; E – elytral punctures; F – mesoventrite, lateral view; G – male metaventrite; H – female metaventrite. Scale I: 1 mm for A and B; II: 0.5 mm for D; III: 0.5 mm for F; IV: 1 mm for G and H." ;
